basicInfo.name: Catty
basicInfo.flavor: She once attacked Jin out of her feral instinct, but quickly lost the fight. She started to follow him and began to train under his tutelage.

Normal Attack.desc:
Single Enemy
 - Deals damage equal to 100% of Physical Attack 1 time(s).
Skill Enhancement Effect
 - Increases Damage: To 120% of Physical Attack.

Skill 1.name: Claw Attack
Skill 1.desc:
Single Enemy
 - Deals damage equal to 230% of Physical Attack 1 time(s).
 - 100% chance to inflict Unable to Recover. [Duration: 4 Turn(s)]
 - 100% chance to inflict Physical Vulnerability. [Duration: 5 Turn(s)]
Skill Enhancement Effect
 - Increases Damage: To 270% of Physical Attack.
Transcend Lv.2 Effect
 - Adds Effect: 100% chance to inflict 33% Block Rate Reduction. [Duration: 5 Turn(s)]

Skill 2.name: Expose Weakness
Skill 2.desc:
All Allies
 - Grants Crit Rate Boost. [Duration: 3 Turn(s)]
Skill Enhancement Effect
 - Increases Effect: Crit Rate Boost to 27%.
Transcend Lv.6 Effect
 - Adds Effect: 32% Weakness Hit Chance Boost. [Duration: 3 Turn(s)]

Passive.name: Sharp Claws
Passive.desc:
Self
 - Grants Physical Attack Boost. [Duration: 3 Turn(s)]
Skill Enhancement Effect
 - Increases Effect: Physical Attack Boost to 31%.

profile.likes: Jin, cats, Coco, Lina, freedom, fun things, curiosity, sashimi
profile.story: Over time, Catty came to understand how she was different from the cats that raised her. Still, she chose to stand by her feline protectors, shutting out the world of humans.
